      1          /**
      2           *  @file
      3           *  @brief      Detect max, min and peak to peak value taken from defined number of samples.
      4           *
      5           *  @details    Extremes searching is performed within each handled in function #PeakDetector__SetValue period.
      6           *              New calculation (min, max and peak to peak values) are available after defined (in function #PeakDetector__Setup)
      7           *              number of period samples.
      8           *              Each new calculation will be available thought function
      9           *              #PeakDetector__GetMin, #PeakDetector__GetMax, #PeakDetector__GetPeak2Peak.
     10           *
     11           *              e.g. If each new value is set every 1ms,
