    194           * Set new rough value used for peak detector calculation, and handle it.
    195           * New calculation are available after defined (in function #PeakDetector__Setup)
    196           * number of period samples are set.
    197           * Each new calculation will be available thought function
    198           * #PeakDetector__GetMin, #PeakDetector__GetMax, #PeakDetector__GetPeak2Peak.
    199           *
    200           * e.g. If each new value is set every 1ms,
    201           * and period value is defined to 20 samples than every new calculation will be available
    202           * every 20ms.
    203           *
